reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It’s a space saver
reviews.reviewText: I don’t like people to have to reach sideways to get TP. I had been using a regular freestanding toilet paper holder but the bottom roll always gets a little dirty. So I saw this and thought it was perfect! TP is in front of the toilet where it belongs. (I also didn’t want to mount something on the wall).It is slim and just right!Pretty piece! Easy to put together.Just bought a 2nd one for the other bathroom.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Small, Sleek & Sturdy!
reviews.reviewText: I read several of the reviews before making my decision to purchase this stand and I can say it does not disappoint! I use it as a small nightstand next to my bed in a small space and its perfect! The included assembly instructions do lack slight direction but construction is still fairly intuitive. My only recommendation when putting it together is to make sure you have the metal side metal brackets connected in a way that places the holes for the back supporting wood panel on the side of top shelf that is facing the back and not the front where the top shelf has an opening! Sleek looking shelf, Im glad I purchased it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy to set up. But was missing a piece.
reviews.reviewText: This table is perfect for the small space I have. Its sturdy so far and was able to put it together while on bed rest so very easy to set up.Only complaint I have is that it was missing the back board that holds up books you put in it. Which is part of why i bought it in the first place..Everything else is exactly like the photos.
